				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Soloing tactics that still work?<a name="65533"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 4 04 10:07 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi, I'm new to the bardic profession, about level 30 now.  I know I always start a class too late, I heard there's been some nerfs, but what solo tactics are still viable?  Which ones can be done by a 30ish bard?  Thanks!</span></td>
