				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Soloing tactics that still work?<a name="65535"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 4 04 10:15 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>With any weapon from the bazaar and a fungi tunic you can solo to 50's just straight mele.  This will max all your skil-ups from the mele and max your instrument skills fromt he songs you play on the side.
<br />

<br />
I meled from 1 to 53.  If you don't have lots of regen (can't buy a fungi) the process just has you killing a wee bit slower.
<br />

<br />
Sol a was nice at low levels. Lots of mobs, and a good experience bonus in the zone.  
<br />

<br />
moose</span></td>
