				<td colspan="2"><span>Since you didn't say solo exp techniques, I'd add that you can melee/mez/heal any mob that can be mezzed and does not regen faster than you can kill.
<br />

<br />
People does this with mobs like Phinny in their 60s (usually 65 though :p).
<br />

<br />
But you can really do fine with any mob that can be mezzed.  It would also go along with the poster suggesting melee.
<br />

<br />
You might really like pulling.  I do.  In that case try some ldons or outdoor zones like OT.</span></td>
